{"tid":1488554,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[置頂] 樣樣都做先可以令呢場運動繼續","createTime":"2019-08-19T16:01:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T16:24:48.000Z","uid":73959,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c3fbf69c18c33a52ad580a12576d81bc9dfac9b3","tid":1488554,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:01:30.000Z","msg":"<strong>1. <ins>和理非遊行集會要繼續</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n和理非佔大部分人數係事實<br />\n下下都衝撃 佢哋點上場幫手？<br />\n大家要俾啲機會佢哋付出下<br />\n先可以keep住佢哋嘅involvement<br />\n冇和理非<br />\n邊到有100萬 200萬 170萬人數你去造勢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>2. <ins>勇武依然要勇武</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n要運動成功 必須有人犧牲<br />\n有人肯冒住生命危險、被捕風險行岀嚟<br />\n先至可以一步一步將政府、黑警同中共魔爪呈現出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>3. <ins>文宣繼續升級</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>文宣=凝聚力</strong></span></span><br />\n係非常非常之重要<br />\n冇文宣 遊行可以吹到咁大雞？<br />\n冇文宣 義士嘅血汗可會被看見？<br />\n<br />\n如果想呢場運動繼續熱度唔減直至勝利<br />\n呢三大重點不可缺一<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>樣樣都要做 不停loop！</strong></span></span><br />\n形式上有變化會更加好<br />\n<br />\nE.g.<br />\n和理非 : 遊行集會 &gt; 不合作運動 &gt; ??<br />\n勇武 : 反抗 &gt; 衝擊 &gt; ??<br />\n文宣 : 吹雞 &gt; 分化藍絲 &gt; 輸出革命 &gt; ??<br />\n<br />\n不過最好係咩呀？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">不分和勇宣</span></span>呀！<br />\n<br />\nLv 1 人人都可以係和理非<br />\nLv 2 人人都可以做文宣<br />\nLv 3 人人都可以勇武<br />\n<br />\n喺自己能力範圍盡做啦好冇？<br />\n<br />\nBtw我屌哂你班咸濕仔老母呀<br />\n一開連登個個post都講嗰個老藕狗乸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n五大訴求呢？爆眼義士呢？800人被捕呢？721呢？被斬到見骨嗰巴打呢？被起底嘅機師空姐空少醫護人仕呢？死咗嗰6個烈士呢？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你對唔對得住佢哋呀？</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"1dc256834524f9fa2ff26e5641145e6498fd6201","tid":1488554,"uid":73959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:04:22.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">BUC GOK JEK<br />\nBUC DUK FUI<br />\nBUC FEN FA</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">KWONG FUK HERN KONG<br />\nSI DOI GAK MING</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">NG DAI SO KAU<br />\nKUET YUT BUC HOR<br />\n</span><br />\n</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U8F2BvC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU8F2BvC.png&h=c74d6f75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZsOSYJ1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZsOSYJ1.png&h=3e5059d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CNwUsCp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCNwUsCp.png&h=5d9a7a23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XAhkoaN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXAhkoaN.png&h=5622300c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7a15zhx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7a15zhx.png&h=9a897094&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>人人都可以係文宣！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"920d63be49b0c548e490ed08a6b184a0db6370f7","tid":1488554,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:04:36.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"809f397c78def30f3c9a0875913c363fb5a94be3","tid":1488554,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:04:55.000Z","msg":"8.22死線。毋分和勇，永不割席：終極行動原則 2.0 + FAQ<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1488447\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1488447</a>"},{"pid":"fd5e62cb2f6ea3e95289891dd7e057b709a66cce","tid":1488554,"uid":43668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:07:13.000Z","msg":"正經po"},{"pid":"6cc6b4c939d831116f9b2e8f2ad1c52e9e35